# VHS tape for release-scholar
# Run: vhs assets/demo.tape
# Requires: https://github.com/charmbracelet/vhs
#
# Edit the commands below to demonstrate your tool's core workflow.

Output assets/demo.gif

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Dracula"

Type "release-scholar --help"
Enter
Sleep 2s

